39
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,100
SPEAKER_04: Sure there's no mistake?

40
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:23,579
SPEAKER_04: Look at the records.

78
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:20,819
SPEAKER_04: Can't rush these things.

79
00:08:21,060 --> 00:08:25,089
SPEAKER_04: Fengxia's growing up. Another's on the way.

99
00:10:20,009 --> 00:10:21,909
SPEAKER_04: Master Fugui, you lost.

100
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,590
SPEAKER_04: Let's roll!

126
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:56,950
SPEAKER_04: for leaving you homeless.

164
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:37,269
SPEAKER_04: No, Fugui's signature is on each one.

165
00:17:39,019 --> 00:17:42,950
SPEAKER_04: Long'er, is our Xu family home...

167
00:17:47,319 --> 00:17:49,160
SPEAKER_04: Good.

168
00:17:51,130 --> 00:17:55,829
SPEAKER_04: A gambling debt's a debt,
and debts must be paid.

187
00:19:55,250 --> 00:19:58,549
SPEAKER_04: I'll look after her for a few days?

188
00:19:58,690 --> 00:20:00,920
SPEAKER_04: Until you're set up elsewhere.

226
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:07,099
SPEAKER_04: Master Fugui! It's been a year at least.

244
00:25:17,539 --> 00:25:19,529
SPEAKER_04: Put together a troupe.

245
00:25:21,210 --> 00:25:22,910
SPEAKER_04: They are fabulous.

246
00:25:25,349 --> 00:25:28,250
SPEAKER_04: My heart is full of sorrow

247
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:46,339
SPEAKER_04: It's that hateful bandit, Jiang

248
00:26:02,690 --> 00:26:08,619
SPEAKER_04: I'm lucky to be alive

638
01:13:27,800 --> 01:13:30,130
SPEAKER_04: He hadn't slept for three days.

639
01:13:56,729 --> 01:13:58,420
SPEAKER_04: Fugui, listen to me.

734
01:24:02,600 --> 01:24:05,500
SPEAKER_04: Let's not bring up the past.

735
01:24:09,939 --> 01:24:12,930
SPEAKER_04: Burn them, okay?
I've got other people to see.

912
01:41:22,140 --> 01:41:23,329
SPEAKER_04: Really?

913
01:41:23,939 --> 01:41:28,000
SPEAKER_04: I just came from the hospital.
