914
01:41:29,939 --> 01:41:32,239
SPEAKER_04: Fengxia's going to be a mother.

926
01:42:14,460 --> 01:42:16,119
SPEAKER_04: He was very busy?

944
01:43:25,989 --> 01:43:28,829
SPEAKER_04: He's been arrested as a capitalist.

945
01:43:29,000 --> 01:43:31,829
SPEAKER_04: They held a public trial against him.

946
01:43:32,069 --> 01:43:34,930
SPEAKER_04: We have to draw a line between us and him.

1062
01:52:01,170 --> 01:52:02,159
SPEAKER_04: Yes, us!

1063
01:52:02,239 --> 01:52:03,399
SPEAKER_04: I mean, older ones.

1071
01:52:37,439 --> 01:52:39,239
SPEAKER_04: Have to get one out.

1086
01:54:03,300 --> 01:54:05,289
SPEAKER_04: That's professor Wang...

1087
01:54:05,500 --> 01:54:07,229
SPEAKER_04: head of obstetrics.

1166
02:00:00,789 --> 02:00:02,380
SPEAKER_04: What's with him?

1167
02:00:11,630 --> 02:00:13,390
SPEAKER_04: He ate too quickly.

1262
02:07:42,550 --> 02:07:44,180
SPEAKER_04: Not just buns...

1263
02:07:44,279 --> 02:07:46,310
SPEAKER_04: anything made from wheat.

